OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773702670
OL,3,CUK looking at a 'viable plan' to open
OL,4,Cthe Strait of Hormuz, Starmer says
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer said on Monday that
OL,7,Fhe is working with allies on a plan to
OL,8,Freopen the Strait of Hormuz as the
OL,9,Fconflict in the Middle East continues
OL,10,Fto drive up global oil prices.
OL,12,FReplying to a question from ITV News'
OL,13,FPolitical Editor Robert Peston on
OL,14,Fwhether the UK will heed US President
OL,15,FDonald Trump's call to send the Royal
OL,16,FNavy to the major trade route in the
OL,17,FMiddle East, the PM said there have
OL,18,Fbeen "discussions ongoing" with global
OL,19,Fpartners.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773702670
OL,3,CUK looking at a 'viable plan' to open
OL,4,Cthe Strait of Hormuz, Starmer says
OL,6,F"It is not straightforward, and
OL,7,Ftherefore we have to make sure that
OL,8,Fwe've got that credible plan in place
OL,9,Fas to what the precise options are,"
OL,10,Fhe told reporters at a Downing Street
OL,11,Fconference.
OL,13,F"This isn't just about what the UK can
OL,14,Fdo, it's about how we play a part in
OL,15,Fbringing others together behind a
OL,16,Fviable plan. So that's where we're at
OL,17,Fthe moment," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773702670
OL,3,CUK looking at a 'viable plan' to open
OL,4,Cthe Strait of Hormuz, Starmer says
OL,6,FStarmer did not say what options are
OL,7,Fbeing considered amid questions over
OL,8,Fwhether the UK could deploy further
OL,9,Fmilitary provision to the region.
OL,11,FHe said that British involvement in
OL,12,Fany action was "something (he)
OL,13,Fdiscussed" with Trump on the phone
OL,14,Fover the weekend.
OL,16,FHis comments come after Trump said
OL,17,Fthat NATO faces a "very bad" future
OL,18,Fshould its member states fail to
OL,19,Fsecure the critical waterway for
OL,20,Fglobal oil shipping.
