OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773702670
OL,3,CUK looking at a 'viable plan' to open
OL,4,Cthe Strait of Hormuz, Starmer says
OL,6,FThe PM also insisted he would not
OL,7,Fallow the UK to be drawn into a "wider
OL,8,Fwar" in the Middle East because of the
OL,9,Fknock-on impacts on the cost of living
OL,10,Fin the UK.
OL,12,FOil costs have soared in response to
OL,13,Fthe war in Iran, which began with
OL,14,Fjoint Israeli-US strikes on February
OL,15,F28.
OL,17,F"The longer this goes on, the more
OL,18,Fdangerous the situation becomes and
OL,19,Fthe worse it is for the cost of living
OL,20,Fback here at home," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
