FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773702670
OL,3,CUK looking at a 'viable plan' to open
OL,4,Cthe Strait of Hormuz, Starmer says
OL,6,FStarmer announced a #53 million plan
OL,7,Fto ease the cost of living pressures
OL,8,Fin the UK, targeted at customers who
OL,9,Fare "most exposed" to the consequences
OL,10,Fof rising oil and gas prices,
OL,11,Fincluding those who rely on heating
OL,12,Foil.
OL,14,FHe also revealed the government will
OL,15,Fgive "legal direction" to make sure
OL,16,Fenergy companies pass on savings to
OL,17,Ftheir customers, "to keep bills as low
OL,18,Fas possible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
