CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773702670
OL,3,CUK looking at a 'viable plan' to open
OL,4,Cthe Strait of Hormuz, Starmer says
OL,6,FLast week, the Chancellor met with
OL,7,Fenergy companies to warn them against
OL,8,F"profiteering" - following concerns
OL,9,Fthat companies could use the current
OL,10,Fcrisis to put up prices unfairly and
OL,11,Fmake a profit.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
