PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773702670
OL,3,CUK looking at a 'viable plan' to open
OL,4,Cthe Strait of Hormuz, Starmer says
OL,6,F"I simply will not allow companies to
OL,7,Fmake huge profits from the hardship of
OL,8,Fworking people. This government was
OL,9,Felected to stop that. And we will," he
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FBut in his press conference, the PM
OL,13,Finsisted that the long-term answer to
OL,14,Fenergy security was "home-grown"
OL,15,Fenergy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
