PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773702670
OL,3,CUK looking at a 'viable plan' to open
OL,4,Cthe Strait of Hormuz, Starmer says
OL,6,F"Until we get ourselves off the roller
OL,7,Fcoaster of international oil and gas
OL,8,Fmarkets and onto clean, home-grown
OL,9,FBritish energy, tyrants like Putin and
OL,10,Fthe Ayatollahs will be free to attack
OL,11,Four energy security," he warned.
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
